docs/superpowers/

# This repo's LIVE per-run session state is never tracked.
journal/session/

# Do NOT ignore templates/journal/session/ — in this template repo the session seed
# (current.md, archive/.gitkeep) MUST be tracked so it ships via npx/npm pack and
# `grimoire init`/seedRoot can seed it. Target projects get the session ignore from
# templates/gitignore-snippet.txt, which `grimoire init` writes into their .gitignore.
